{"tid":432953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"川榮李奈為政府宣傳眾議院選舉","createTime":"2017-10-12T03:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T04:40:19.000Z","uid":44569,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7d119bcf6df12a95ca72d37379969792a9caeb","tid":432953,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://kenshin.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/senate-vote.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkenshin.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsenate-vote.jpg&h=715f7721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n川榮李奈不經不覺已成為AKB48畢業生中發展最好的，近期除了參演大熱的au三太郎廣告，今次還當上眾議院選舉投票廣告的主角，要知道政府廣告對演出者形象要求很高，也代表了她的實力。不過政府廣告果然是安全至上，你會覺得這CM平凡到不像充滿創意的日本廣告。因為這次選舉所以富士月9要延播一星期，而當中有份參演的正是過去AKB48的一姐&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XlothdJw5I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXlothdJw5I0&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9f11e62a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XlothdJw5I0</a><br />\n<br />\n眾議院議員總選舉 官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.soumu.go.jp/2017senkyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.soumu.go.jp%2F2017senkyo%2F&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=de05e93d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.soumu.go.jp/2017senkyo/</a>"},{"pid":"71c68be124de4c5c002f128da11e05e36310efdf","tid":432953,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"政府走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}